data.title: Download – Overture Maps Foundation
data.text: Overture’s 2024-07-22.0 data release and v1.0.0 of the schema are now available. The base, buildings, divisions, and places themes have reached General Availability (GA). The transportation theme remains in beta, and users can anticipate additional breaking changes to the transportation schema. Also in this release, we launched a new theme called addresses, available in alpha. We will be making significant changes to the addresses schema and updating and adding to the addresses data over the next several months.
